Value PS_ID (\d+)
Value PS_TYPE (.+?)
Value PS_STATUS (\S+)
Value FAN_ID (\d+)
Value FAN_STATUS (\S+)
Value SENSOR_NAME (.+?)
Value TEMP ([\d.]+)
Value MAC_TYPE (.+?)
Value MAC_ADDR (\S+)

Start
  ^Power\s+supply\s+${PS_ID}\s+\(${PS_TYPE}\)\s+present,\s+status\s+${PS_STATUS} -> Record
  ^Fan\s+${FAN_ID}\s+${FAN_STATUS}, -> Record
  ^${SENSOR_NAME}\s+Temperature\s+Readings: -> Continue
  ^\s+Current\s+temperature\s+:\s+${TEMP}\s+deg-C -> Record
  ^${MAC_TYPE}\s+MAC\s*:\s*${MAC_ADDR} -> Record
